##########################
> Design Document
##########################
> Problem Definition
    - retiring KED
    - create a tool to crack documents to text for consumption using LUIS.
      This was initially done using KED internally but it got cut from the public preview.

> Use Cases
    - LUIS-D
        - extract text from documents before submitting to LUIS-D

> Proposal
    - overview
        - what the app does
            - mainly extracts text from documents (docs or scans)
        - scope
            - documents (pdf, word, text, ppt, ..)
            - scans (images, scanned pdfs, ..)
        - how to use
            - this tool is supposed to be a web server
            - users can run them locally, or deploy to a hosting service

    - apis
        - api/parseAll
            - description
                - parse all docs in source Blob store and stores extracted text in tagret Blob store
            - header
                - Connection-String
                    - azure blob store key
            - parameters
                - sourceContainerName
                - destinationContainerName
            - response
            
        - api/parseSingle
            - description
                - parse single doc in source Blob store and stores extracted text in tagret Blob store
            - header
                - Connection-String
                    - azure blob store key
            - parameters
                - sourceContainerName
                - destinationContainerName
                - fileName
            - response

        - api/container/{containerName}/blobs
            - description
                - list all files in given blob store
            - header
                - Connection-String
                    - azure blob store key
            - parameters
                - containerName
            - response

    > architecture
        - apis
            - api/parseAll
            - api/parseSingle
            - api/container/{containerName}/blobs
        - controllers
            - storage
            - performance
            - parser
        - services
            - storage
            - parser (TIKA)
